promotionsCarouselChildren.description:
Promo Instructions:
1. Place a cash wager on any market or game available on theScore Bet. 
2. If your wager settles as a loss, get 100% of your wager back, up to $1,000 paid out as five (5) separate Bonus Bets.

The “$1,000 Bet Reset” (“Promotion”) is subject to the Promotional Terms and Conditions (“Promotion Terms”) of theScore Bet, which can be viewed at thescore.bet/legal/promo-terms, and the following: 

Eligibility:  
Participants must be at least 19 years of age or older. Participants must be physically located in the province of Ontario. Participants must have a valid payment method to fund their account. Participants must have a valid and active theScore Bet account.  

Promotion Period:  
The Promotion may be redeemed only one (1) time during the Promotion Period. The Promotion Period is as follows:  
June 3, 2024: 12:00:00 AM ET – September 30, 2024: 11:59:59 PM ET 

Qualifying Action:  
Participants must place a cash wager on any market or game available on theScore Bet during the Promotion Period to qualify for the Promotion Reward (“Qualifying Bet”). To qualify for the Promotion Reward (as defined below), the Qualifying Bet must settle as a loss. The first Qualifying Bet made during the Promotion Period will be used to determine the value of the Promotion Reward.  

Participants who settle the Qualifying Bet using the “Cash Out” feature will not receive the Promotion Reward. In accordance with the Promotion Terms, if the Qualifying Bet is deemed “No Action” in accordance with the Betting Rules (at thescore.bet/help/house-rules), then the Promotion Reward will not be awarded. Opt-in is required. A wager placed using a Bonus Bet will not qualify.  

Promotion Reward:  
The “Promotion Reward” is 100% of the Qualifying Bet amount, up to $1,000 paid out in five (5) Bonus Bets each valued at 20% of the wager if the Qualifying Bet settles as a loss. The Promotion Reward is loaded to player’s Accounts within 72 hours from the end of the Promotion Period and must be used within seven (7) days after receipt. The Promotion Reward is non-transferable. The Promotion Reward cannot be redeemed for cash. The Promotion Reward cannot be withdrawn. The Promotion Reward cannot be cashed out. The Promotion Reward is limited to one (1) per account. 

Promotion Exclusions:  
The Promotion may not be combined with any other promotion unless otherwise specified.  

Customer Support:  
For any questions, please visit thescore.bet/help. You may also contact theScore Bet directly at 1 (855) 550-1238 or support@thescore.bet. 

FAQ:  
For more information on Bonus Bets, Bonus Spins and Eligible Cashback, please visit thescore.bet/help/how-to-bet.   

Responsible Gaming:  
19+. ON only. If you or someone you know has a gambling problem, call ConnexOntario 24/7 at 1-866-531-2600. Text us at 247247 or chat with us at www.connexontario.ca.

promotionsCarouselChildren.description:
The “$1,000 First Deposit Match Bonus” (“Promotion”) is subject to the Promotional Terms and Conditions (“Promotion Terms”) of theScore Bet, which can be viewed at thescore.bet/legal/promo-terms, and the following:


Eligibility: 
Participants must be at least 19 years of age or older. Participants must be physically located in the province of Ontario. Participants must have a valid payment method to fund their account. Participants must have a valid and active theScore Bet account. Participants must have not made a deposit on theScore Bet as of the start of the Promotion Period. 


Promotion Period: 
The Promotion will start on 2024/02/01 and end on 2024/09/30 (“Promotion Period”). The Promotion may be redeemed only one (1) time during the Promotion Period.


Qualifying Action: 
Participants must make their first-ever deposit of $10 or more on theScore Bet (“Qualifying Deposit”), during the Promotion Period to qualify for the Promotion Reward (as defined below). The first Qualifying Deposit made during the Promotion Period will be used to calculate the value of the Promotion Reward. Opt-in is not required.


Promotion Reward: 
The “Promotion Reward” is Eligible Cashback valued at 100% of the Qualifying Deposit amount, up to a maximum Eligible Cashback value of $1,000. The Eligible Cashback will unlock into cash at a rate of 5% of the wagered amount (cashback is rounded up or down to the nearest cent) on Sportsbook cash bets at greater than -200 odds (e.g. -110 odds or +200 odds would qualify) (“Sportsbook Cashback Rate”) and at a rate of 1% of the wagered amount (cashback is rounded up or down to the nearest cent) on Casino cash bets on any available Casino games in theScore Bet (“Casino Cashback Rate”). Participants will have thirty (30) days from the date they receive the Eligible Cashback to unlock the balance into cash (“Cashback Period”). Participants who cash out of any wager that was used to unlock the Eligible Cashback will have the corresponding amount of unlocked Eligible Cashback revert back from cash to the Eligible Cashback balance. That amount may be unlocked again by placing a cash bet if the Eligible Cashback is still available during the Cashback Period. Eligible Cashback is "available" if its redemption period has not expired, the amount has not been fully claimed, has not been opted out of, or has not otherwise been revoked in accordance with the Promotion Terms. Any Eligible Cashback balance that remains locked at the end of the Cashback Period will be forfeited. The Promotion Reward is non-transferable. The Promotion Reward is limited to one (1) per account.


Cashback Example: 
A Participant has made a Qualifying Deposit of $1,000 and has an active Eligible Cashback of $1,000. The Participant can unlock cashback over the next thirty (30) days on both Sportsbook and Casino wagers. This cashback unlocks at a rate of 5% (cashback is rounded up or down to the nearest cent) for Sportsbook cash bets (greater than -200 odds) and 1% (cashback is rounded up or down to the nearest cent) for Casino cash bets on available games - win or lose. For example, if the Participant makes a Sportsbook cash bet of $500 with odds of +200, the Participant will receive $25 back into their withdrawable Cash balance while $25 will be subtracted from the Eligible Cashback balance. If the Participant then places a Casino cash bet on an eligible game of $100, the Participant will receive $1 back into their withdrawable Cash balance while $1 will be subtracted from the Eligible Cashback balance. Any Eligible Cashback balance that remains locked at the end of the Cashback Period will be forfeited and any Eligible Cashback balance that was already unlocked will not be revoked.  


Promotion Exclusions: 
The Promotion may not be combined with any other promotion unless otherwise specified. VIP-designated players are not eligible for this Promotion. 


Customer Support: 
For any questions, please visit thescore.bet/help. You may also contact theScore Bet directly at 1 (855) 550-1238 or support@thescore.bet.


FAQ: 
For more information on Bonus Bets, Bonus Spins and Eligible Cashback, please visit thescore.bet/help/how-to-bet.  


Responsible Gaming: 
19+. ON only. If you or someone you know has a gambling problem, call ConnexOntario 24/7 at 1-866-531-2600. Text us at 247247 or chat with us at www.connexontario.ca.

Referees have 30 days to complete the Qualifying Action to receive the Promotion Reward (as defined below).

The Promotion Reward will be issued immediately upon completion of the “Qualifying Action” by the Referee, or in the event of technical difficulties, within 72 business hours and must be used within seven (7) days after receipt. The Promotion Reward is non-transferable. The Promotion Reward cannot be redeemed for cash. The Promotion Reward cannot be withdrawn. The Promotion Reward cannot be cashed out. September 16, 2024: 9:00:00 AM ET - September 22, 2024: 11:59:59 PM ET 


Ineligible Wagers: 
Participants who settle a Qualifying Bet using the “Cash Out” feature will not have that wager count towards the total Qualifying Bets criteria. In accordance with the Promotion Terms, if a Qualifying Bet is deemed “No Action” in accordance with the Betting Rules (at thescore.bet/help/house-rules), then that wager will not count towards the total Qualifying Bets criteria. Weekly opt-in is required. Parlays with less than four (4) legs will not qualify. Parlays containing legs with odds shorter than -500 will not qualify. A SGP wager will not qualify.
